            <h3>Olongapo City’s Must Do List</h3>
            <ol>
                <li>1. Night life at Ramon Magsaysay Drive.</li>
                <li>2. Visit the City Museum</li>
                <li>3. Avail of the audio visual presentations of the different city’s programs like the HELPS (Health and Housing, Educa- tion and Environment, Livelihood and Labor, Peace and Order and Social Welfare and Sports), Solid Waste Management System, Color Coding of Public Transportation, and Child Friendly City among others.</li>
                <li>4. Take pleasure in swimming in the pristine beaches of Olongapo</li>
                <li>5. Enjoy shopping for souvenir items in shops located at Olongapo City Public Market and the Gawang Gapo Product Exhibit at the lobby area of Olongapo City Hall.</li>
            </ol>
